            "short_description": "Gritty Bit VR is a VR shooter where the player assumes control of an anti-virus and is dropped into a computer infested with dangerous viruses. Using the unique movement system, you will traverse the 3D landscape within the computer, dodge enemy projectiles and destroy the deadly viruses.",
